# Test Scope

- Do not write new tests or update existing tests unless the user explicitly asks for tests.
- Do not run automated tests, test scripts, or test-related CLI commands unless the user explicitly asks.
- Do not include test work in plans, suggested implementation steps, or default follow-up actions unless the user explicitly requests it.
- If tests would normally be the next step, mention that they were intentionally skipped because the user did not ask for them.
